登宣布美国将从阿富汗撤军。截至 7 月初，驻阿富汗美军的撤军工作已完成了 90%，拜登政府预计，撤军工作将于 8 月 31 日前完成。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-bfb067783a7d6c9e3fa2840fdbe700a1_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/472379731"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ig/3uvuecv79dEAMaCDY3MjUyNjgyIPDIv4cGMBs47QRAJHIJNDcyMzc5NzMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1626481316.1133096", "card_id": "Q_466252124", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 171}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么埃及金字塔能耸立 4600 年？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "距今 1000 多年的楼兰，高昌古国已被沙漠掩埋，距今 800 多年的临安古城也是考古学家挖掘出来的。成都平原上明代 4，5 百年前的王陵，只要没有人维护，就会消失在历史的长河中，靠历史学家去搜寻才能重现…。题主认为古埃及的金字塔位于靠近大海的沙漠地带，风沙及腐蚀性远大于内陆，早就会被埋掉或腐蚀掉！但它却居然能够耸立 4600 年？这样的事情，为什么会有人相信？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-5a763802f46942b176c35ba16af5b173_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/466252124"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ig/3uvuecv79dEAMaCDY1ODkxMjk2IOq8v4YGME044wdAJXIJNDY2MjUyMTI0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1626481316.1140783", "card_id": "Q_460533239", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1371}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "会跟喜欢的人结婚还是门当户对的?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-804294f484e6045f2bf75d45a37442cc_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "37 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/460533239"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ig/3uvuecv79dEAMaCDY0NjIwNTA1IIbFmYUGMAw4mg5AJnIJNDYwNTMzMjM5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id":